    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>A May 21 letter writer is correct about the universality and generally high quality of the child care system in France. But I would like to mention the staggering rates of taxation there, combined with levels of government intervention in personal and business life that might well give many Americans pause.</p>
        <p>SAUL D. RAW  Brooklyn, May 21, 2000</p>
      </block>
